You don't have to hire someone

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:18.320
who has the experience of

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:20.440
cooking because the processes are

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:22.080
so standardized, so key-in-hand

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:23.520
that you can file anyone

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:24.920
without any experience.

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:29.640
And the first day is already making

